sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import CreateOutlinedIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CreateOutlined' import DeleteOutlineOutlinedIcon from '@mui/icons-material/DeleteOutlineOutlined' function ReadOnlyRow({contact, handleDelete, handleEditRowId}) { return ( {contact.name} {contact.email} {contact.phone} handleDelete(contact._id)} style={{ color: "red", cursor: "pointer", }} /> ) } export default ReadOnlyRow
